description:
In this Everything Iconic POP Dive, Danny welcomes Courtney Frain (of the Two Judgey Girls podcast/Instagram) & Whitney to talk about 2006's The Devil Wears Prada (film). They discuss the movie's impact, favorite fashion moments, the future of the franchise, and so much more.


*For bonus episodes & to support this podcast, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
